\begin_inset Formula $\E_{\random y|\random x}(\random y|\random x)=x\pi$
\end_inset

 which has variance 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda\pi^{2}$
\end_inset

 so that the right hand side adds to 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda\pi$
\end_inset

, the variance of 
\begin_inset Formula $\random y$
